@startuml

actor User

participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "REST API" as REST
participant "GraphQL API" as GraphQL
database "MySQL Database" as DB

== REST Flow ==

User -> Frontend : Open Books Page

Frontend -> REST : GET /api/books

REST -> DB : SELECT * FROM books

DB --> REST : Books Data

REST --> Frontend : JSON Response

Frontend --> User : Display Books

== GraphQL Flow ==

User -> Frontend : Open GraphQL Demo

Frontend -> GraphQL : Query books { title author }

GraphQL -> DB : SELECT title, author FROM books

DB --> GraphQL : Filtered Data

GraphQL --> Frontend : GraphQL Response

Frontend --> User : Display Books

@enduml